This version of rosjava (https://github.com/rosjava/rosjava_core) has been modified
from its original source. This notices describes all changes and lists the 
affected files.

To support interoperability with the google-collections (https://code.google.com/p/google-collections) 
and guava libraries (https://code.google.com/p/guava-libraries), the following source files 
have been modified:
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/DefaultMessageInterfaceClassProvider.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/StringFileProvider.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/StringResourceProvider.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/context/MessageContextProvider.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/definition/MessageDefinitionFileProvider.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/definition/MessageDefinitionReflectionProvider.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/concurrent/ListenerGroup.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/concurrent/RetryingExecutorService.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/server/ParameterServer.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/server/master/MasterRegistrationManagerImpl.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/service/ServiceManager.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/topic/TopicParticipantManager.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/transport/ConnectionHeader.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/transport/ConnectionTrackingHandler.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava_geometry/src/main/java/org/ros/rosjava_geometry/FrameTransformTree.java

In addition, several modifications have been made to the ROS service implementation to enhance its flexibility.
The following source files have been modified for these service changes:
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/field/ChannelBufferField.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/concurrent/DefaultScheduledExecutorService.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/server/master/MasterServer.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/service/DefaultServiceClient.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/service/DefaultServiceServer.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/service/ServiceFactory.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/service/ServiceManager.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/node/service/DefaultServiceClientListener.java (added)
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/node/service/ServiceClient.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/node/service/ServiceClientListener.java (added)

Fixed a bug in the ParameterServer implementation that incorrectly labels some graph names as invalid:
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/server/ParameterServer.java

Enabled XML-RPC multicall requests:
   rosjava_core/apache_xmlrpc_server/src/main/java/org/apache/xmlrpc/server/XmlRpcStreamServer.java

Ensured that "null" inputs to array message field setter functions are correctly handled:
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/field/BooleanArrayField.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/field/ByteArrayField.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/field/DoubleArrayField.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/field/FloatArrayField.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/field/IntegerArrayField.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/field/LongArrayField.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/field/ShortArrayField.java

Made sure that publishers are re-added by existing subscribers if they are re-created:
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/topic/DefaultSubscriber.java

To avoid lengthy DNS lookups in some network configurations, changed the following file:
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/address/InetAddressFactory.java

Fixed a bug in the serialization and deserialization of fixed-size message arrays.
The following files are affected:
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/field/ListField.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/field/MessageFieldType.java
   rosjava_bootstrap/message_generation/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/message/field/PrimitiveFieldType.java

Added an interface to node objects, so the user can determine if simulation or wall clock time is used.
The following files are affected:
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/DefaultNode.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/node/ConnectedNode.java

Adjusted the ParameterTree implementation, so it handles parameter names that are invalid
ROS graph names correctly. Affected files:
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/client/ParameterClient.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/parameter/DefaultParameterTree.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/namespace/GraphName.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/node/AnonymousParmeterTree.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/node/parameter/ParameterTree.java

Enabled the TCP_NODELAY option for all TCP/IP connections to alleviate performance
problems on Windows machines. See the affected files:
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/service/ServiceDeclaration.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/topic/TopicDeclaration.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/transport/tcp/TcpClient.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/transport/tcp/TcpRosServer.java

Ensured error-free shutdown behavior for the DefaultNode and made the shutdown timeouts
for publisher, subscriber, service client, service server, and node public properties. See
the affected files:
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/DefaultNode.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/service/DefaultServiceClient.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/service/DefaultServiceServer.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/topic/DefaultPublisher.java
   rosjava_core/rosjava/src/main/java/org/ros/internal/node/topic/DefaultSubscriber.java

